name: City Runner 102
description:
City Runner 102
PNG 5000 x 5000 px

The unique rendered output of an algorithm exploring the (non)-intersection of line segments. Every iteration a horizontal or vertical line is drawn without intersecting any of the already existing lines. In this study the lines on the horizontal axis are tilted resulting in a more dynamic and (retro-)futuristic look. The margin around the most dense area is expanded to generate some additional breathing space.
